ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T13:46:33.000Z","msg":"加油呀<br />\n我得個位數都仲生存緊<br />\n你得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34a91b4967823d3b5908e76c45a6cd5ffd959274","tid":318944,"uid":11526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:01:49.000Z","msg":"如果讀書唔適合你咪早d出黎做野囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d803c6904717d2afee5088f4426a40ba9d2ca937","tid":318944,"uid":119504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:03:08.000Z","msg":"第一，有半年時間仲要溫通頂&hellip;一係你既能力值18分，一係方法錯左，當然壓力都係問題。<br />\n第二，問題出現左，應該要諗辦法解決。<br />\n校方，唔係問題，無視。朋友，唔係問題，係朋友唔會宜家踩你，踩你既朋友放生佢啦。<br />\n屋企好大問題，後補。<br />\n自己問題，其實成件事都只關你事&hellip;自己問題即係前路迷茫&hellip;<br />\n其實唔迷茫，得兩條路，一入大學，一唔入大學。入大學方法你知既比我多。唔入大學多數都要挨。<br />\n你想做咩？你可以做啲咩？你真係做到?做到後你得到咩？係咪你開始想要既咩？始想等於終得，做。<br />\n屋企問題，其實屋企係關心你前途&hellip;諗定左自己既前路，同屋企人傾下，一份希望，兩份計劃，<del>七份幻想</del>，能醫百病。<br />\n日子難過，訓一訓又過一日，最多咪訓多幾日。"},{"pid":"fd2fda15aab3ad936a32d35338e6ee42660ba2b4","tid":318944,"uid":75148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:03:31.000Z","msg":"讀唔到未出黎做野囉 唔洗死架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc8359ded26a81e9ab550ba5fafb63c8c3eda5e7","tid":318944,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:04:20.000Z","msg":"我20 sor<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Loser"},{"pid":"ecb9e857730f97325f55addb7a543811dd06cc0e","tid":318944,"uid":31173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:05:07.000Z","msg":"真心，有決心既可考慮retake ，但有心理準備呢一年會唔好過，捱過左就上大學"},{"pid":"b58e294f3c828ed4b96ad44e4f486916ad27ff24","tid":318944,